TowerScout YOLO-Enabled Release Licensing

This file describes the intended license posture for the TowerScout
YOLO-enabled release track. It is not a substitute for final owner/legal
approval, and it does not remove stricter notices in individual files.

TowerScout-authored code:

TowerScout-authored source code that is confirmed as project-owned is intended
to be distributed under the Apache License, Version 2.0. If a file carries a
different notice, or if ownership has not been confirmed, that file remains
subject to its existing notice until release review resolves it.

YOLO-enabled distribution:

The current detector runtime includes Ultralytics YOLOv5 source code vendored
under webapp/vendor/yolov5_local/. That source is governed by the GNU Affero
General Public License, Version 3.0, as shown in
webapp/vendor/yolov5_local/LICENSE. The YOLO-enabled package and container
image are therefore distributed with AGPL-3.0 obligations. Do not describe the
full YOLO-enabled runtime distribution as Apache-2.0-only.

Model and data assets:

Model weights and ZIP-code data are governed by the model and data terms in
MODEL_LICENSES.md and DATA_LICENSES.md. The YOLO detector weights are treated
as YOLO-derived/AGPL-governed for this release track unless a separate written
model license or permission record says otherwise.

Provider terms:

Google Maps, Azure Maps, and any other provider APIs are external services.
Their terms are not granted by this repository license. See PROVIDER_TERMS.md.

Release notices:

See NOTICE and THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md for the source offer, third-party
attribution, and package-level compliance notes.
